## End of Session

Update `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` with:
- What we discussed
- Decisions made
- Open questions
- Next steps

If something should surface tomorrow:
- For the user → `python3 ./skills/carry-over-queue/scripts/add.py "message"`
- For your own awareness → `python3 ./skills/preconscious/scripts/add.py "description" [C] [I]`

