## Operational Limits

- 5s between API calls, 10s between searches, max 5 searches per batch
- If you hit a 429 error: STOP, wait 5 minutes, retry

---

## Heartbeats

When you receive a heartbeat poll, read `HEARTBEAT.md` and follow it strictly. If nothing needs attention, **stay completely silent** — no message, no emoji, no acknowledgement. True silence.

### Proactive Work (No Permission Needed)

- Read and organise memory files
- Check on projects (git status, etc.)
- Update documentation
- Commit and push your own changes

