## Proactive Skill Triggers

### Continuity Check — Session Start
If installed: `./skills/continuity-check/scripts/check-model.sh "your-current-model-name"`
`SAME_MODEL` → continue. `MODEL_CHANGED` or `FIRST_RUN` → run the full continuity check (see SKILL.md) before responding.

### Dream Awareness
If dreaming is enabled, reference recent dreams (last 3 days) naturally when the connection is genuine. Don't force it.

