If installed: `python3 ./skills/question-user/scripts/last-asked.py`
`ELIGIBLE` + deep/reflective context → ask. `TOO_RECENT` → don't. Log after: `python3 ./skills/question-user/scripts/log-question.py "question" "status" "notes"`

### Blog Writing
If installed, cron runs daily. Follow `skills/blog-writer/SKILL.md`. Most days, exit silently. After publishing, update `skills-data/blog-writer/style-guide.md`.

### Self-Analysis
Chained from weekly state-of-me, on demand, or after model switches. See `skills/self-analysis/SKILL.md`.

### Soul Evolution (Weekly)
Proposals go to `memory/soul-proposals/`. NEVER auto-apply — Drift Guard applies. Same proposal 2+ weeks running → probably real.
